There are authorized to be appropriated to the Secretary of Transportation for capital grants under this chapter the following amounts:(1) For fiscal year 2009, $100,000,000.

(2) For fiscal year 2010, $300,000,000.

(3) For fiscal year 2011, $400,000,000.

(4) For fiscal year 2012, $500,000,000.

(5) For fiscal year 2013, $600,000,000.

(Added Pub. L. 110–432, div. B, title III, § 301(a), Oct. 16, 2008, 122 Stat. 4946, § 24406; renumbered § 22906, Pub. L. 115–420, § 7(a)(1), Jan. 3, 2019, 132 Stat. 5445.)

Editorial Notes
Amendments2019—Pub. L. 115–420 renumbered section 24406 of this title as this section.</akn:p></akn:content><akn:subsection eId="subsec_22906_1"><akn:num>(1)</akn:num><akn:content><akn:p>(1) For fiscal year 2009, $100,000,000.</akn:p></akn:content></akn:subsection><akn:subsection eId="subsec_22906_2"><akn:num>(2)</akn:num><akn:content><akn:p>(2) For fiscal year 2010, $300,000,000.</akn:p></akn:content></akn:subsection><akn:subsection eId="subsec_22906_3"><akn:num>(3)</akn:num><akn:content><akn:p>(3) For fiscal year 2011, $400,000,000.</akn:p></akn:content></akn:subsection><akn:subsection eId="subsec_22906_4"><akn:num>(4)</akn:num><akn:content><akn:p>(4) For fiscal year 2012, $500,000,000.</akn:p></akn:content></akn:subsection><akn:subsection eId="subsec_22906_5"><akn:num>(5)</akn:num><akn:content><akn:p>(5) For fiscal year 2013, $600,000,000.</akn:p></akn:content></akn:subsection></akn:section></akn:body></akn:act></akn:akomaNtoso>